===Noun===
'''greenhouse''' (''plural'' '''greenhouses''')

#A building made of [[glass]] in which [[plant]]s are [[grow]]n more [[rapidly]] than outside such a building by the action of [[heat]] from the [[sun]], this heat being trapped inside by the glass.

